836. Sci Rep. 2023 Sep 19;13(1):15500. doi: 10.1038/s41598-023-42578-0.

Recent natural selection conferred protection against schizophrenia by 
non-antagonistic pleiotropy.

González-Peñas J(1)(2)(3), de Hoyos L(4)(5)(6), Díaz-Caneja CM(4)(5)(7)(8), 
