Premature morbidity and mortality associated with potentially undiagnosed 
familial hypercholesterolemia in the general population.

Ray KK(1), Pillas D(2), Hadjiphilippou S(1), Khunti K(3), Seshasai SRK(4), 
Vallejo-Vaz AJ(1)(5)(6), Neasham D(2), Addison J(7).

Author information:
(1)Imperial Centre for Cardiovascular Disease Prevention (ICCP), Dept. of 
Primary Care and Public Health, School of Public Health, Imperial College 
