Practice and development of male contraception: European Academy of Andrology 
and American Society of Andrology guidelines.

Wang C(1), Meriggiola MC(2), Amory JK(3), Barratt CLR(4), Behre HM(5), Bremner 
WJ(3), Ferlin A(6), Honig S(7), Kopa Z(8), Lo K(9), Nieschlag E(10), Page 
